text: I love this restaurant a lot. It has a romantic feeling. The food is superb. the service is effective and the waiters are professional. The cost is reasonable. I highly recommend.

name: Shareen Franklin
text: The young men very friendly and nice. The kids said the pizza was really good. Thank you for the great customer service and fast service.

name: Desirae Harrison
text: This location is terrible. I have used up the remaining "rewards" and I won't be back. I'd say 7 out of 10 times my order has been wrong. Just irritating.

name: Kenneth Wieczorek
text: I visit this excellent restaurant once a month because I love the  special atmosphere that is exist in this restaurant. The team is awfuly welcoming and skilfull. The service is extremely rapid. Also, the food they cook is excellent. I …More

text: They are apparently satisfied with their "quality Control" wherein it is ok to provide the customer with burnt pizza and bread sticks.  it's not ok.

text: GM Richard made things right. Everytime my ranch cup is forgotten,  Richard remembered.

name: Elizabeth Carroll
text: Fast delivery and great pizza.  Thank you!

name: Tommy Seilheimer
text: Just wanted to say we absolutely LOVED our Pizza tonight. Haven't had Papa John's Pizza in years and decided to give it a try. Pizza was perfect. The facility was clean the workers friendly and the Manager was very polite and friendly with customers. We will be back!

name: Dave Schubert
text: My favorite. Use the phone app for special deals. A large 1-topping pizza just $8 in the app.many more deals including a 2-for special.

text: Twice for carry out this week ,  the clothes from the people nasty, the place does no look as should be, I thought they have to were wearing kind of uniform. There are people making pizzas and attending customers , taking money and no cleaning their hands, maybe that’s why taste is good!!

text: The customer service is always swift, great mood, welcoming staff. Will return here again when I get in the area.

text: Ordered from this location a few days ago, had a large pizza with sausage and pepperoni and it was very tasty, the wings on the other hand weren’t all that great but the pizza made up for it, will order again soon

text: Tried calling four times to order and didn't get an answer. Guess they don't want my money.

text: Terrible delivery person and cold stale pizza. The box was cold in a 76 degrees and sunny day. I'm only 4 minute drive. It was gross. The toppings were chewey and dethawed in a microwave maybe? Gross. All gross. Such a waste of money.

name: Mickinite cool guy mike

name: Timothy Coon
text: I travel the country with my job, and this location has the rest (including my home town) beat hands down! I ordered my normal... Wings, bacon cheese bread... Sauces and soda... Service was prompt.. food was hot and perfectly prepared..and soda was cold... Great job folks!

name: Scott Bell
text: The pizza itself is very good, but the service is extremely lacking. Orders are frequently made wrong, wrong pizzas delivered more than once, and once wasn't delivered at all and when a trip was made to pick up the non delivered order it …More

text: Never had any problems. Their rewards system is fantastic, free stuff every few orders. Best "cheap" pizza in my opinion.
